description:
#### New package name: **[tabby](https://chocolatey.org/packages/tabby)**

---

`terminus` has been deprecated because the software has been rebranded to Tabby. 

It exists only for backward compatibility to provide a transitional dummy package for existing users and scripts which may still use this package ID.
summary: Terminus is a web technology based terminal heavily inspired by Hyper.
author: Eugene Pankov (and contributors)
